TASK_DESCRIPTION=The Go TUI currently has separate Activity, Interactions, and Logs tabs. Consolidate Activity and Interactions into the Logs tab as sub-sections or filterable views. Remove the standalone Activity and Interactions tabs from the tab bar. The Logs tab should show all three data streams — logs, activity, and interactions — either as sub-tabs within Logs or as a single merged chronological view with type labels. Check tui/internal/model/ for the tab definitions and rendering code.
